__data__.text:
assistant: 1. Move to the kitchen area.
2. Open the dark wooden cabinet above the counter.
3. Remove all items from the cabinet.
4. Wipe down the cabinet shelves.
5. Organize the removed items by category.
6. Place baking supplies in the cabinet above the counter.
7. Close the cabinet.
8. Open the dark wooden cabinet below the counter.
9. Remove all items from the cabinet.
10. Wipe down the cabinet shelves.
11. Organize the removed items by category.
12. Place cooking supplies in the cabinet below the counter.
13. Close the cabinet.
14. Move to the refrigerator.
15. Remove all items from the top of the refrigerator.
16. Wipe down the top of the refrigerator.
17. Place the loaf of bread, cereal, and cake or muffin box in the refrigerator or a nearby cabinet.
18. Move to the countertop.
19. Pick up the red and white container near the sink.
20. Place the container in a designated cabinet or on a tray.
21. Wipe down the countertop.
22. Move to the wall cabinet with utensils.
23. Remove any unnecessary items from the cabinet.
24. Organize the utensils in the cabinet.
25. Close the cabinet.
26. Move to the dining area.
27. Pick up the box of cereal from the table.
28. Place the box in a designated cabinet or on a tray in the kitchen.
29. Wipe down the dining table.
30. Move to the cupboard in the corner of the room.
31. Open the cupboard.
32. Remove any unnecessary items from the cupboard.
33. Organize the items in the cupboard.
34. Close the cupboard.
35. Inspect the kitchen and dining area to ensure everything is tidy and in its place.
